{"title":"青花瓷","authors":["段和平"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青花瓷（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密林幽涧中的泉韵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催开簇簇冷艳的山花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烘托一种氛围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有经历高温的苦楚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能凝成这泥土的精华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇山异水的灵秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稀释后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓游动于瓷身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年的时光抖落尘埃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为生动的立体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似一抹傲岸的霞彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在心之一隅闪烁光华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古琴与夜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是清冽的夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在半梦半醒之间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月影轻移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寂静如雾缓缓漫开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗被抚慰得微醺的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诠释一种千年的期待。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玄奥在地下深埋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现实的顿悟却被描出形来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那音韵如轻柔的夜风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊溅起不可言传的天籁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀揣这如泣如诉的呵护，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才发觉已迷失了来路。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}